The paper also mentions the successful application of self-paced learning strategy in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with image classification tasks, which falls under the sub-categories cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
